_sText:
_When the void comes, what was once familiar beauty is at risk of being lost.
Our blocks turn to static; our air: full of holes._

My first bhop map.
Short, somewhat difficult.
Prespeed is occasionally required, although most parts can be done without it.

Designed for 100 tick, should work with 200/auto/ez.
Uses Millet's multihop, Aoki's prefab.
